title: Honey-Soy Chicken & Roast Kumara Toss with Japanese Mayo & Crushed Peanuts
description: The magic in this dish is the juicy chicken thigh, perfectly browned and then drizzled with our tasty Japanese mayo.
Add a nourishing roasted kumara salad and some crushed peanuts in the mix, and you've got an Asian-inspired meal in no time!

